1
00:00:05,666 --> 00:00:08,362
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,435 --> 00:00:12,303
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,373 --> 00:00:16,366
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,710 --> 00:00:19,201
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,279 --> 00:00:23,272
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,350 --> 00:00:27,377
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,856 --> 00:00:33,589
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,294 --> 00:00:37,263
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,700 --> 00:00:41,793
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,536 --> 00:00:43,833
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,171 --> 00:00:46,731
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,648 --> 00:01:00,143
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,254 --> 00:01:01,516
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,588 --> 00:01:05,388
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,726 --> 00:01:10,925
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,198 --> 00:01:12,495
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,566 --> 00:01:13,999
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14,067 --> 00:01:20,336
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:40,101
I'm going to be Hokage!

20
00:01:41,276 --> 00:01:44,677
I won't lose here!

21
00:01:44,946 --> 00:01:48,939
Whatever! You can't keep up
with my speed at all!

22
00:01:51,186 --> 00:01:51,914
U!

23
00:01:55,924 --> 00:01:57,516
Zu! Ma! Ki!

24
00:02:02,664 --> 00:02:04,154
Naruto Barrage!

25
00:02:23,752 --> 00:02:25,913
The winner is Naruto Uzumaki.

26
00:02:28,356 --> 00:02:31,985
<i>I'm...getting stronger!</i>

27
00:02:32,894 --> 00:02:35,089
Ohhhh!

28
00:02:35,363 --> 00:02:36,625
Cha!

29
00:02:36,831 --> 00:02:39,664
Nice one! You did it!

30
00:02:40,402 --> 00:02:43,098
T-That Naruto beat Kiba!

31
00:02:43,838 --> 00:02:45,567
It's a major upset...

32
00:02:45,740 --> 00:02:46,434
Yup!

33
00:02:48,677 --> 00:02:49,336
<i>Yes!</i>

34
00:02:50,545 --> 00:02:56,484
Byakugan Battle: Hinata Grows Bold!

35
00:03:00,589 --> 00:03:03,422
This medicine works really well!

36
00:03:05,293 --> 00:03:07,591
Here! Do you want to
use it too, Sakura?

37
00:03:10,098 --> 00:03:14,228
<i>Only your wounds heal</i>
<i>with such speed...Naruto.</i>

38
00:03:15,303 --> 00:03:18,739
<i>The power of Nine Tail never</i>
<i>ceases to amaze me.</i>

39
00:03:32,887 --> 00:03:34,411
U-Umm...

40
00:03:43,598 --> 00:03:45,759
T-This is...

41
00:03:45,834 --> 00:03:46,766
ointment for your wound,

42
00:03:47,402 --> 00:03:49,302
for you Kiba and Akamaru.

43
00:03:52,540 --> 00:03:53,632
Rather than worrying about others,

44
00:03:53,708 --> 00:03:55,699
it's about time you worried
about yourself!

45
00:03:56,778 --> 00:03:57,335
Kiba...

46
00:03:58,513 --> 00:03:59,639
There are only 6 people left...

47
00:03:59,881 --> 00:04:05,820
you, Choji, Neji, Lee, one Sound guy,
and the Sand guy.

48
00:04:07,455 --> 00:04:08,945
Listen, Hinata...

49
00:04:11,192 --> 00:04:14,127
If you pull that guy from Sand,
withdraw quickly.

50
00:04:15,063 --> 00:04:16,553
And there's one more...

51
00:04:17,332 --> 00:04:18,993
Do the same if you get Neji, too.

52
00:04:19,934 --> 00:04:20,798
Withdraw quickly...

53
00:04:22,337 --> 00:04:23,770
That guy will be hard on you.

54
00:04:24,806 --> 00:04:26,068
He will destroy you.

55
00:04:27,242 --> 00:04:29,938
Well, let's announce the next match.

56
00:04:30,512 --> 00:04:31,137
- Huh?
- Huh?

57
00:04:31,479 --> 00:04:32,070
- What?
- Huh?

58
00:04:38,453 --> 00:04:39,852
Hinata Hyuga vs. Neji Hyuga

59
00:04:44,526 --> 00:04:45,185
<i>Hinata...</i>

60
00:04:46,127 --> 00:04:49,585
<i>This is going to be an interesting match...</i>

61
00:05:06,381 --> 00:05:09,544
I never thought that I would
have a fight with you...

62
00:05:10,118 --> 00:05:11,016
Lady Hinata.

63
00:05:11,786 --> 00:05:12,684
Brother Neji...

64
00:05:13,221 --> 00:05:14,119
Brother?

65
00:05:14,556 --> 00:05:15,181
Huh?!

66
00:05:15,557 --> 00:05:17,650
Those two are siblings?

67
00:05:23,365 --> 00:05:24,332
They're descended from

68
00:05:24,399 --> 00:05:27,493
one of the most honorable
old families in the Hidden Leaf...

69
00:05:27,769 --> 00:05:28,963
The Hyuga Clan.

70
00:05:29,938 --> 00:05:31,963
But, they're not siblings.

71
00:05:32,307 --> 00:05:34,537
Then, how are they related?

72
00:05:38,146 --> 00:05:41,411
Well, the relation of a head family
and branch family...

73
00:05:41,483 --> 00:05:43,280
That may be an appropriate
way to say it.

74
00:05:44,319 --> 00:05:45,809
Head family and branch family?

75
00:05:46,488 --> 00:05:47,011
Yes!

76
00:05:47,922 --> 00:05:50,117
Hinata is from the head family.

77
00:05:50,558 --> 00:05:52,526
In other words, a person from
the main household

78
00:05:52,761 --> 00:05:55,855
and Neji is from a branch family
that is descended from that family.

79
00:05:56,297 --> 00:05:59,289
In other words,
it's a fight between relatives.

80
00:05:59,801 --> 00:06:01,962
It must be uneasy for both of them...

81
00:06:02,437 --> 00:06:02,903
Yes.

82
00:06:03,671 --> 00:06:04,194
However...

83
00:06:04,606 --> 00:06:06,073
Huh? What is it?

84
00:06:06,875 --> 00:06:08,467
I've heard that from long ago,

85
00:06:08,543 --> 00:06:10,568
there've been various incidents between
the head family and branch family,

86
00:06:10,779 --> 00:06:13,543
and now their relationship
isn't on very good terms.

87
00:06:14,282 --> 00:06:15,442
Hmmm.

88
00:06:15,784 --> 00:06:16,512
Why?

89
00:06:16,618 --> 00:06:18,449
I don't know the details either.

90
00:06:18,887 --> 00:06:19,376
Only...

91
00:06:20,288 --> 00:06:24,486
The so called distinguished Ninja clans
like Uchiha and Hyuga

92
00:06:24,893 --> 00:06:27,862
have special techniques and
abilities that run in the family.

93
00:06:28,596 --> 00:06:31,429
It seems that the Hyuga household
laid down rules

94
00:06:31,499 --> 00:06:33,592
for communicating those techniques...

95
00:06:34,569 --> 00:06:37,003
It seems that there are many rules
that favor the head family...

96
00:06:37,539 --> 00:06:38,267
- Huh?
- Huh?

97
00:06:39,140 --> 00:06:40,573
And there have been
various incidents

98
00:06:40,642 --> 00:06:43,634
between the head family and
branch family due to those rules.

99
00:06:45,980 --> 00:06:48,642
So this is a confrontation billed
as a clash of fate...

100
00:06:56,758 --> 00:06:58,521
Oh, it's gonna begin.

101
00:06:59,694 --> 00:07:02,094
Start the battle please!

102
00:07:04,833 --> 00:07:07,734
Just one thing before we square off
against each other in the fight...

103
00:07:07,802 --> 00:07:09,827
I should advise you, Lady Hinata.

104
00:07:11,072 --> 00:07:11,970
Withdraw!

105
00:07:12,740 --> 00:07:14,765
You're not suited to being a Shinobi.

106
00:07:18,546 --> 00:07:19,911
You're too nice.

107
00:07:20,882 --> 00:07:23,442
You wish for harmony and
avoid conflict,

108
00:07:24,018 --> 00:07:26,543
you're open to going with
the thinking of others.

109
00:07:28,256 --> 00:07:31,225
And, you have no confidence
in yourself.

110
00:07:32,060 --> 00:07:34,085
You're always feeling inferior...

111
00:07:34,696 --> 00:07:37,256
You thought it's a good idea
to stay Genin.

112
00:07:38,166 --> 00:07:41,693
However, you can't register for
the Chunin test without three members...

113
00:07:42,403 --> 00:07:45,531
So you couldn't turn down when Kiba
and the other proposed it and,

114
00:07:45,740 --> 00:07:48,834
the truth is, you entered
the exam reluctantly.

115
00:07:49,811 --> 00:07:50,505
Is that wrong?!

116
00:07:50,845 --> 00:07:52,176
T-That's wrong...

117
00:07:52,647 --> 00:07:53,511
That's not true...

118
00:07:54,215 --> 00:07:54,943
I...

119
00:07:55,650 --> 00:07:56,844
I only...

120
00:07:58,086 --> 00:07:59,815
I wanted to change that about myself...

121
00:07:59,888 --> 00:08:00,752
So I proposed it myself...

122
00:08:08,096 --> 00:08:08,790
<i>Hinata...</i>

123
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:21,071
Stand up, Hanabi!

124
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:28,548
From now on, I'll keep Hinata
under my wing...

125
00:08:29,317 --> 00:08:31,683
But is that really okay?

126
00:08:34,689 --> 00:08:37,180
Hinata should be the heir to
the Hyuga clan...

127
00:08:37,926 --> 00:08:41,362
But, there is always death involved
with the job of Genin.

128
00:08:42,997 --> 00:08:44,259
Do what you want.

129
00:08:46,334 --> 00:08:50,202
She's a failure who's inferior even to her
younger sister Hanabi, five years her junior.

130
00:08:50,471 --> 00:08:52,564
We don't need her here
in Hyuga clan...

131
00:09:00,381 --> 00:09:02,144
Is that all you have to say?

132
00:09:02,984 --> 00:09:04,212
If so, leave!

133
00:09:04,886 --> 00:09:05,784
You're in the way!

134
00:09:06,788 --> 00:09:07,379
Yes.

135
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:22,765
<i>Hinata is trying to change</i>
<i>herself in her own way.</i>

136
00:09:33,681 --> 00:09:34,511
Lady Hinata...

137
00:09:35,383 --> 00:09:37,874
You are a spoiled one of
the head family.

138
00:09:39,387 --> 00:09:41,855
People can never change!

139
00:09:43,858 --> 00:09:45,826
A failure will <i>always</i> be a failure...

140
00:09:46,461 --> 00:09:49,328
That personality and strength
won't change.

141
00:09:54,435 --> 00:09:55,493
<i>That guy...</i>

142
00:10:01,576 --> 00:10:04,704
Since people don't change,
differences exist among them...

143
00:10:05,079 --> 00:10:08,310
and expressions like "elite"
and "failure" are born.

144
00:10:09,417 --> 00:10:11,044
Everyone judges and are judged

145
00:10:11,119 --> 00:10:13,280
based on the value of their face and
brain, ability and body type,

146
00:10:13,354 --> 00:10:16,790
good and bad points of
their personalities.

147
00:10:17,659 --> 00:10:20,025
People have to suffer and live

148
00:10:20,094 --> 00:10:24,087
within the means of the
elements they cannot change.

149
00:10:26,034 --> 00:10:27,433
Just like the fact that I'm from a
branch family

150
00:10:27,502 --> 00:10:29,834
and you're from the head family,

151
00:10:29,904 --> 00:10:31,496
these things can't change.

152
00:10:34,075 --> 00:10:37,340
I've seen everything with
this Byakugan.

153
00:10:38,379 --> 00:10:39,277
That's why I understand!

154
00:10:40,014 --> 00:10:41,311
You're just talking tough.

155
00:10:42,650 --> 00:10:46,245
You're really thinking that you'd
like to run away from this place...

156
00:10:47,388 --> 00:10:48,582
T-That's wrong...

157
00:10:48,890 --> 00:10:50,118
I really...

158
00:10:50,625 --> 00:10:51,489
Byakugan?

159
00:10:52,060 --> 00:10:54,790
It's said that if you trace
the Uchiha Clan's history,

160
00:10:54,929 --> 00:10:57,659
the clan's ability has its source
in Hyuga clan.

161
00:10:58,833 --> 00:11:03,532
The Byakugan is one of the
Hyuga clan's Kekkei Genkai,

162
00:11:04,138 --> 00:11:05,935
a Visual Jutsu similar
to Sharingan...

163
00:11:06,774 --> 00:11:09,834
However, with the ability of insight alone...

164
00:11:09,944 --> 00:11:12,139
it gets the better of Sharingan.

165
00:11:23,958 --> 00:11:24,947
Byakugan!

166
00:11:27,119 --> 00:11:29,986
Hinata Hyuga vs. Neji Hyuga

167
00:12:19,004 --> 00:12:20,665
My eyes can't be deceived.

168
00:12:22,341 --> 00:12:23,501
Just now from my pressure,

169
00:12:23,809 --> 00:12:28,178
your line of sight was pushed
to the upper left.

170
00:12:29,681 --> 00:12:32,912
This is the sign that you're recalling
your past experience...

171
00:12:33,552 --> 00:12:35,042
your bitter past.

172
00:12:36,154 --> 00:12:39,681
And soon after that, your line of sight
moved to the bottom right...

173
00:12:40,659 --> 00:12:45,687
This is the sign that you're imagining
physical and mental suffering.

174
00:12:46,565 --> 00:12:47,190
That means...

175
00:12:48,166 --> 00:12:49,997
you're picturing your old self,

176
00:12:50,369 --> 00:12:51,893
and from all of your experiences
up until now,

177
00:12:52,104 --> 00:12:54,334
you're imagining the result
of this battle...

178
00:12:55,774 --> 00:12:57,901
The image of you losing!

179
00:13:07,319 --> 00:13:10,686
Even the act of propping your arms
in front of your body...

180
00:13:11,723 --> 00:13:13,554
It's a gesture that means

181
00:13:13,792 --> 00:13:16,693
you want to build a wall
between us and keep distant.

182
00:13:18,263 --> 00:13:19,662
And that reflects your mind...

183
00:13:19,731 --> 00:13:22,723
that you don't want any more
of your deepest feelings to be raided...

184
00:13:23,969 --> 00:13:26,665
Because everything I've said
is right on the mark, right?

185
00:13:28,640 --> 00:13:29,402
Furthermore...

186
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:36,438
Laying a finger on your lips,

187
00:13:36,581 --> 00:13:39,846
that too, is a self-familiarizing act
which represents a sense of panic.

188
00:13:41,353 --> 00:13:43,583
It represents a defense instinct

189
00:13:43,655 --> 00:13:45,987
you want to alleviate the tension
and unease.

190
00:13:47,559 --> 00:13:48,321
In other words...

191
00:13:49,261 --> 00:13:51,957
deep in your heart,
you know it's true, don't you?

192
00:13:54,166 --> 00:13:57,192
Changing yourself,
is something you absolutely can't do!

193
00:13:57,269 --> 00:13:58,099
Sure, she can!

194
00:14:07,045 --> 00:14:09,809
You don't have the privilege of
deciding what a person is like, stupid!

195
00:14:10,182 --> 00:14:12,241
Give it to him, Hinata!

196
00:14:16,521 --> 00:14:17,385
<i>Naruto...</i>

197
00:14:26,264 --> 00:14:27,231
Hinata!

198
00:14:27,766 --> 00:14:29,757
Don't just take it!
Argue back!

199
00:14:30,068 --> 00:14:31,968
I'm getting irritated watching this!

200
00:14:48,453 --> 00:14:49,283
<i>Naruto...</i>

201
00:14:50,989 --> 00:14:52,513
<i>What an annoying guy!</i>

202
00:14:59,631 --> 00:15:00,393
<i>Naruto...</i>

203
00:15:03,435 --> 00:15:04,197
<i>Thank you!</i>

204
00:15:09,407 --> 00:15:10,635
<i>The expression of her eyes</i>
<i>has changed...</i>

205
00:15:12,310 --> 00:15:13,607
So you're not going to withdraw?

206
00:15:13,979 --> 00:15:15,503
I'm not taking responsibility
for what happens!

207
00:15:16,782 --> 00:15:17,578
<i>I...</i>

208
00:15:20,118 --> 00:15:21,585
<i>I won't run away!</i>

209
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:23,116
<i>I don't...</i>

210
00:15:23,755 --> 00:15:26,121
<i>I don't change my words...</i>

211
00:15:26,691 --> 00:15:28,249
<i>That's my Way of Ninja!</i>

212
00:15:29,694 --> 00:15:30,752
<i>...want to run anymore!</i>

213
00:15:32,497 --> 00:15:33,395
Byakugan!

214
00:15:44,442 --> 00:15:45,409
Brother Neji!

215
00:15:46,611 --> 00:15:47,373
I challenge you!

216
00:15:48,513 --> 00:15:49,241
<i>T-That is...</i>

217
00:15:59,958 --> 00:16:00,982
Fine...

218
00:16:06,097 --> 00:16:08,088
Of course, the same Hyuga style...

219
00:16:09,034 --> 00:16:10,899
Her pose is very similar
to Neji's.

220
00:16:11,436 --> 00:16:12,403
Hyuga style?

221
00:16:13,538 --> 00:16:16,166
The strongest Taijutsu style
in the Village Hidden in the Leaf...

222
00:16:16,241 --> 00:16:16,832
Huh?

223
00:16:17,642 --> 00:16:18,939
I said it before...

224
00:16:20,011 --> 00:16:22,036
The man who is most likely

225
00:16:22,113 --> 00:16:25,310
the strongest Genin of Hidden
Leaf Village is on my team...

226
00:16:26,084 --> 00:16:26,743
That's...

227
00:16:27,452 --> 00:16:29,010
That guy, Neji Hyuga.

228
00:17:14,566 --> 00:17:16,864
<i>Here!</i>

229
00:17:26,645 --> 00:17:27,236
Did it go in?!

230
00:17:27,512 --> 00:17:29,377
No... it was shallow!

231
00:17:29,581 --> 00:17:32,482
No. Even a graze works.

232
00:17:33,418 --> 00:17:34,942
That's the reason that the Hyuga clan

233
00:17:35,020 --> 00:17:37,352
is called the Hidden Leaf's
distinguished family.

234
00:17:37,689 --> 00:17:39,486
Huh? What do you mean?

235
00:17:39,958 --> 00:17:44,395
The Hyuga has a particular
Taijutsu passed down through generations.

236
00:17:48,900 --> 00:17:51,391
It's not like the kind of Taijutsu that
Lee and I are good at...

237
00:17:51,469 --> 00:17:54,870
Our way of fighting, Furious Fist,

238
00:17:54,940 --> 00:17:58,706
is mainly to inflict external damage
on our enemy,

239
00:17:58,777 --> 00:18:00,768
like broken bones and surface wounds.

240
00:18:01,713 --> 00:18:04,238
In contrast, the Hyuga's Taijutsu
inflict damage

241
00:18:04,316 --> 00:18:06,614
on the Chakra Network through
which Chakra flow through the body,

242
00:18:06,685 --> 00:18:10,587
and damaging the insides,
namely, it destroys internal organs.

243
00:18:11,056 --> 00:18:12,956
They possess the Gentle Fist.

244
00:18:14,225 --> 00:18:15,817
It's not spectacular to watch...

245
00:18:16,428 --> 00:18:18,191
but later it slowly takes effect.

246
00:18:19,331 --> 00:18:22,630
Well, you can't train the internal organs...

247
00:18:23,301 --> 00:18:24,859
Even if you were really robust,

248
00:18:24,936 --> 00:18:26,961
one hit from it would be
a deadly blow...

249
00:18:39,184 --> 00:18:40,014
<i>Even I can...</i>

250
00:18:42,087 --> 00:18:43,281
<i>Hinata's on the offensive...</i>

251
00:18:44,489 --> 00:18:45,148
<i>Hinata...</i>

252
00:18:47,625 --> 00:18:49,820
Way to go, Hinata!

253
00:18:50,428 --> 00:18:52,259
To attack the Chakra Network...

254
00:18:53,198 --> 00:18:55,189
What are they, those people...?

255
00:18:57,035 --> 00:18:57,626
Hey!

256
00:18:57,802 --> 00:18:58,393
Hey!

257
00:18:58,703 --> 00:19:01,194
Chakra Network, what's that?!

258
00:19:01,439 --> 00:19:02,599
Here we go again...

259
00:19:02,674 --> 00:19:04,107
a question from a stupid guy.

260
00:19:04,909 --> 00:19:06,069
I'll explain.

261
00:19:07,145 --> 00:19:08,407
They're like blood canals.

262
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:10,778
In the same way that blood flows
through vessels throughout the body,

263
00:19:10,849 --> 00:19:16,810
They're bundles of canals that take
Chakra's into every corner of your body...

264
00:19:17,489 --> 00:19:18,547
Oh!

265
00:19:18,623 --> 00:19:20,955
Like a path for Chakras, huh?

266
00:19:21,259 --> 00:19:21,884
Yes...

267
00:19:22,527 --> 00:19:24,017
Furthermore, the Chakra Network
is closely connected

268
00:19:24,095 --> 00:19:28,225
with the internal organs which
enfold Chakra within the body.

269
00:19:28,833 --> 00:19:31,199
That's why if
the Chakra Network is attacked

270
00:19:31,369 --> 00:19:33,633
the internal organs also suffer damage.

271
00:19:34,172 --> 00:19:36,941
Huh, you know a lot, don't ya?

272
00:19:36,941 --> 00:19:39,501
Hey you!
That's no way to talk to your senior!

273
00:19:50,622 --> 00:19:51,589
<i>It's no wonder...</i>

274
00:19:52,590 --> 00:19:54,717
<i>Lee's greatest long standing enemy.</i>

275
00:19:55,093 --> 00:19:56,060
<i>That's...</i>

276
00:19:56,161 --> 00:19:56,923
<i>him.</i>

277
00:19:59,030 --> 00:19:59,894
Sensei...

278
00:20:00,131 --> 00:20:02,224
But, how can they do that?

279
00:20:02,867 --> 00:20:06,359
After all, the Chakra Network
isn't visible to the eyes.

280
00:20:06,538 --> 00:20:10,133
How do they attack the Chakra
line inside the body?

281
00:20:10,875 --> 00:20:11,603
No.

282
00:20:12,277 --> 00:20:13,676
The eyes of those two...

283
00:20:14,212 --> 00:20:17,306
They can see it with
their Byakugan.

284
00:20:22,787 --> 00:20:26,621
And a Gentle Fist attack is a little
different from a regular attack.

285
00:20:28,493 --> 00:20:30,188
They release their own Chakra

286
00:20:30,428 --> 00:20:34,922
from a Chakra opening in their hand
and screw it into their opponent's body.

287
00:20:35,266 --> 00:20:38,793
It directly inflicts damage on
your enemy's Chakra Network.

288
00:20:41,439 --> 00:20:42,667
All right!

289
00:20:45,343 --> 00:20:46,241
<i>Has she done it?</i>

290
00:21:06,703 --> 00:21:11,163
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

291
00:21:11,307 --> 00:21:19,646
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

292
00:21:20,650 --> 00:21:29,319
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

293
00:21:29,726 --> 00:21:37,565
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

294
00:21:38,835 --> 00:21:44,239
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

295
00:21:44,307 --> 00:21:48,334
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

296
00:21:48,411 --> 00:21:51,972
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

297
00:21:52,315 --> 00:22:00,848
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

298
00:22:01,124 --> 00:22:06,323
<i>when you want to cry,</i>
<i>and you want to run away</i>

299
00:22:06,395 --> 00:22:10,798
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

300
00:22:10,867 --> 00:22:14,633
<i>Just sing.</i>

301
00:22:14,871 --> 00:22:20,036
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

302
00:22:20,109 --> 00:22:22,304
<i>The two are one</i>

303
00:22:22,411 --> 00:22:28,680
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

304
00:22:29,185 --> 00:22:34,282
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

305
00:22:38,637 --> 00:22:39,604
Amazing!

306
00:22:39,671 --> 00:22:40,763
That Hinata!

307
00:22:40,906 --> 00:22:43,136
She's always melancholy
and wishy washy and...

308
00:22:43,208 --> 00:22:45,176
I thought she is kinda weird, yet...

309
00:22:45,310 --> 00:22:47,608
Even when she gets blow after blow,
she gets back up and goes.

310
00:22:47,813 --> 00:22:49,838
There's something about
her way of fighting.

311
00:22:49,915 --> 00:22:51,212
Just a feeling,
but she resembles you, I think.

312
00:22:51,283 --> 00:22:53,581
Resembles me?
Hinata resembles me?

313
00:22:53,919 --> 00:22:56,513
Now that I think about it, that girl,
she was always watching you.

314
00:22:56,655 --> 00:22:57,212
Huh?

315
00:22:57,689 --> 00:23:00,317
Next episode: "A Failure Stands Tall!"

316
00:23:00,792 --> 00:23:02,487
Hinata, fight!
